title: Looking for diamond+ midlaner
body: Title kinda sums it up ranked 5s team looking for d+ midlaner. You will have to go through a tryout period.

replies.body:
Hi there Lonie! I work for Quintessential eSports and we're looking for anyone who is diamond or above and in oce to apply for our pro team! If you think this is something for you and are looking to take your league up to the next level applications are still open at [www.qtesports.com](http://www.qtesports.com) ! We very much hope you apply! <3
- Thanks QTE team
Added you in game. Interested in trying out.
Ill try out if you havent filled the spot.
